<br>
Shut up please, Belmonte.<br>
<br>
There are places where there are really nice caster loot drops. Chardok, Howling Stones, etc etc etc. As a matter of fact, when I did the Betrayer camp in Chardok the only melee loot we got was a Chokidai spine, which is a random drop throughout the dungeon, and my Betrayer pipe. That was after eight hours straight there. And my group agreed that we had never seen so much loot drop in such a time span. And before you say &quot;oh, well you were only there for your epic piece, since there's no loot for you there you'll never go back,&quot; Chardok is one of my favorite dungeons, I adore it there, and I try to group there whenever possible.<br>
<br>
If you're not hunting the places that drop the caster loot, then you can't bitch.  /who all belmonte usually turns you up in Sebilis.  Try somewhere else, obviously the capital of chain/plate melee Kunark class armor drops isn't going to be the best place for you.<br>
<br>
Besides Belmonte, are you the one up there taking the hits? Melee are far far FAR more gear dependent than casters are. Our gear makes or breaks us, but a caster can survive with minimal gear. I started an Iksar necromancer to see what an INT caster was like. I soloed her to 23 in less than a day, and the only things i put on her were an Advisor robe and a goblin ring I got in SolA once. She wore raw silk other than that. Her viability was not diminished in any way by her lack of gear. Yes, after a certain level the caster should have the highest INT/WIS possible, and yes clerics do take a lot of heal aggro and should have good AC, but Bel, stop bitching so much about loot. If you're naked, you still have your spells, you can still rez and heal, which are your main jobs. If a warrior is naked, you just have a useless lump of flesh until he gets some armor and a sword back in his hand.   A naked monk, while not as helpless as most, will still go down like a paper bag under a waterfall if attacked and feign fails.  Naked rogue, useless except for CR.  Naked wizard, still a damage dealing machine.  Naked enchanter, still able to crowd control in an emergency.  Naked shaman can still land a slow. <p><font size=-2>-Mephy | Master | Tides of Destiny | Torvonnilous</font>

